    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Saw sets in a plane-like stock with an adjustable fence and blade; used to saw rabbets in the edge of a board.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
